          <p>The Steelcase Gesture solves a problem the Aeron and Leap Plus don't fully address: arm support that follows you as you move between a keyboard, touchscreen, phone, and tablet. Its 360-degree armrest system can pivot inward, outward, forward, and at virtually any angle — designed after studying over 2,000 postures across six continents.</p>
